 "accumulateUntil: predicate <[Boolean]> ^ <List[E]> = (\r	| build <ReadWriteStream[E]> |\r\r	build:: self newBuildStream.\r	[ predicate value ]\r		whileFalse: [ build nextPut: self next ].\r	^build contentsWritten\r)",
